sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:null},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:null,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">AI 自动生产、发布神器</span></span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-bottom: 16px;\">\n   <span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">通过 n8n 开源项目，就能配置出一个<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">&nbsp;AI 自动生产内容同步到多平台的神器</span>。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-bottom: 16px;\">\n   <span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">用 AI 批量生产<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">小红书、微博、公众号</span>等多平台文案</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:14px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">的自动化流水线，相当于雇了个 24 小时不休息的 AI 小编，能自动找热点、写文案、调风格，最后还能一键发到各大平台。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:16px;margin-right:8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100040546\" data-ratio=\"0.48148148148148145\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/4e91d9a4-c4b7-43e5-b85c-6a4555f02b00/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/4e91d9a4-c4b7-43e5-b85c-6a4555f02b00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-bottom: 16px;font-size: 16px;\" mpa-font-style=\"matjc6kp3vh\" data-mpa-action-id=\"matjc6l41jer\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">自动解析 YouTube 视频生成摘要</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-bottom: 16px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:14px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">利用GPT-4o-mini&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\" 